Firstly let’s find out how many crabs Monic has compared to Bo. Since it says that Monic has 4 lesser crabs than Bo, we can subtract this difference from what Bo owns which means;
Monic=Bo – 4   =>    7487762 − 4   ⇒     7487758 (number of crabs Monic possesses)
Now since Rani only has ten additional crabs as opposed to Monic , thus ;
Rani=Mono+10        ==>      7487758+10          ⇒         7487768(Number Of Crabs Owed To Rani).
Finally when you add up all their respective collections you get :
Total collection=BO+MO+RA=>        7487762+(7487758)+7487768  ⇒      22463288crabs .

